      "beat_id": "B00",
      "act": "ASK",
      "narration_text": "A guitar string, a diatomic molecule, a laser cavity \u2014 their energies do not vary continuously. They climb a ladder of equally spaced rungs. The bottom rung is never zero. How does a smooth parabola force a staircase?",
