    {
      "beat_id": "B04",
      "t_start": 29.0,
      "estimated_duration_s": 10.0,
      "narration_text": "The trick: define a raising operator a-plus and a lowering operator a-minus. Each one shifts the energy by exactly one unit of h-bar omega \u2014 up or down one rung of the ladder.",
