    {
      "beat_id": "B05",
      "t_start": 39.0,
      "estimated_duration_s": 10.0,
      "narration_text": "The ladder must have a bottom. Energy is a sum of squares and can never go negative. So there exists a ground state that the lowering operator annihilates \u2014 one rung so low that trying to step down finds nothing.",
