      "t_start": 49.0,
      "estimated_duration_s": 11.0,
      "narration_text": "Solving the ground state gives energy one-half h-bar omega \u2014 not zero. The uncertainty principle prevents the particle from sitting still at the bottom of the well. That irreducible jitter is zero-point energy.",
