      "t_start": 60.0,
      "estimated_duration_s": 10.0,
      "narration_text": "Starting from the ground rung, apply the raising operator repeatedly. Each step adds exactly h-bar omega. The full spectrum is E-sub-n equals n plus one-half times h-bar omega. Equally spaced, starting above zero.",
