      "t_start": 70.0,
      "estimated_duration_s": 11.0,
      "narration_text": "The equal spacing is the ladder's key signature. A photon that excites a vibrational mode of a molecule must carry exactly h-bar omega. The infrared absorption spectrum of any diatomic molecule looks like a ruler \u2014 evenly spaced lines \u2014 because the ladder is uniform.",
