      "t_start": 91.0,
      "estimated_duration_s": 9.0,
      "narration_text": "Every smooth trap is a harmonic oscillator in disguise. The energy must be discrete. The spacing is always h-bar omega. And the lowest rung is never zero \u2014 it sits half a step up.",
